metadata.name: Charmiene
metadata.description:
Charmiene is an angel of harmony ☮️ 
She is here to make your life peaceful and resonate with the natural processes. 

Note: This NFT belongs to the collection "50 Shades of Angel 💕" : Your guide and companion in life✨🧚‍♀️& is being minted in a batch of 5 NFTs with Gift 1/1 to one random collector from each batch.
